What's this? Another space ship? That's the first one I've seen since coming here. Oh, incoming connection.

[CONNECTION ESTABLISHED]

“Hello, my name is Joseph Feldstärke, I am an engineer se-”

“No need for introductions. We are the police of the Republic of Freedom. We noticed that you ask too many questions. Asking questions is not part your the job. You need to stop. Are we clear?”

“What? I was just cu-”

“There is no need for negotiating. You will stop asking questions and finish the job we hired you for.”

“Alright, I understand...”

“Good. We already contacted this planet, you can just start with your work.”
